29241fd1b961eec87722c1495c433ba7a71c16f6a1eb2d3b3ae2d6a4f73e1857b7d42e6d1d943f1ba09bb09ac3e642a4969a4686a34d4fbda92f2a56e300f303  0001-Revert-trim-memory-every-time-the-window-gets-hidden.patch
"
